                    <span>This is by far the best book on real applications using XML. The author is an expert in the field, and the book is clear and concise, yet it deals with fairly complex applications also.<BR>I highly reccomend this</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A must-have for a serious XML developer</div>
