                    <span>This book covers the most popular XML application architecture patterns. Great source both for ideas and ready-to-go source code. I was pleasantly surprized to find the whole chapter (Chapter 6: Import from Any Format) devoted to the problem I am facing in my current project... Another excellent book from Marchal that really helps me to do my work.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Practical book - which tells you what you need to know.</div>
