                    <span>This book has many projects, which gives insight into various parts of XML. Basic knowledge of XML is required though. Implementation of these projects is a good way of learning XML. Nothing like hand's on experience.<P>The author's writing style is also good, he gives reasons choosing any particular implementation. <P>If you really need to know XML, buy this book.</span>
                  
              
